[I] Android platform tools

[T] Tools for managing and debugging on the android platform such as: adb,
[T] append2simg, avbtool, e2fsdroid, ext2simg, fastboot, img2simg, lpadd,
[T] lpdump, lpflash, lpmake, lpunpack, make_f2fs, mkbootimg, mkdtboimg,
[T] mke2fs.android, repack_bootimg, simg2img, sload_f2fs, unpack_bootimg.

[U] https://github.com/nmeum/android-tools

[A] Google Inc
[M] NoTag <notag@t2sde.org>

[C] base/x11
[F] CROSS OBJDIR

[L] APL
[V] 36.0.1

[CV-FLAGS] NO-PREFIX
[D] 72bf7917abc63a0493b5db26bf1d635f0dce1bfac022d3080f64a5ac android-tools-36.0.1.tar.xz https://github.com/nmeum/android-tools/releases/download/36.0.1/

var_append cmakeopt ' ' -DOPENSSL_NO_ASM=TRUE
